ConfigFile version 0.2.0
=======================

This module allows to read and write configuration files aka '.ini'.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More
  File::Temp  # for test reason
  Exceptions

